        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-blue-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0">▶</span><span><strong>MU- words:</strong> MUZZY, MUZZLE, MURKY, MUCKY, MUGGY — pair M with U and a strong consonant for consistent scoring</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-blue-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0">▶</span><span><strong>MY- words:</strong> MYTH, MYRRH, MYSTIFY, MYSTIQUE, MYTHIC — the MY combination leverages Y's 4-point value naturally</span></li>
